    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Darkness hides in the recesses of everyone's mind...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A normal man finds himself trapped in an alternate reality enveloped in darkness and twisted, bloodthirsty creatures. Explore and uncover secrets about this aberrant world as you find your way back home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206890/extras/c8de926c8e97c7f5e14db88fa4696884.poster.avif?t=1737961416\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206890/extras/c8de926c8e97c7f5e14db88fa4696884.webm?t=1737961416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206890/extras/c8de926c8e97c7f5e14db88fa4696884.mp4?t=1737961416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A unique take on old-school 3D RPGs, drawing elements from FPS and Parkour games. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore an unnerving, atmospheric world with 5 hours of content. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Precise movement and combat with a high skill ceiling. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find arcane abilities scattered throughout the world and channel the powers of chaos through your sword! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dash and slice through your foes, teleport around the battlefield, and harness the strength of lightning! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10 otherworldly bosses to discover and overcome!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find lost souls and remnants of chaos to upgrade your HP and Damage and transcend into an unstoppable force!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A storyline with many mountains and valleys—gain a second chance at life and save yourself and your loved one from the dark dimension.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206890/extras/630c90630bfa17f0d524c9a9c378077d.poster.avif?t=1737961416\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206890/extras/630c90630bfa17f0d524c9a9c378077d.webm?t=1737961416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206890/extras/630c90630bfa17f0d524c9a9c378077d.mp4?t=1737961416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
